{"tid":725333,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗底褲look射罰球 遭網民嘲笑","createTime":"2018-07-01T16:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T16:34:37.000Z","uid":20634,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d517ee7a98444e779e68b69f4be7f0c3134d8ec4","tid":725333,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/0/730/21995534730/21998918297_600x318.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F0%2F730%2F21995534730%2F21998918297_600x318.jpg&h=e4053685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基斯坦奴朗拿度在對烏拉圭一戰，讓網民看見有趣的一幕，那就是特意拉高短褲至褲襠位置，主射罰球。<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙的基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一向以罰球準繩見稱</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>，當中包括世盃分組賽3:3打和西班牙時，就是憑其罰球追成平手。這名皇家馬德里球星在16強對烏拉圭同樣主射罰球，但C朗在準備主射期間，卻將短褲兩邊褲筒拉高至褲襠位置呈「底褲look」，引來網民在網上熱烈討論和嘲諷。<br />\n<br />\n其中有不少網民以穿著了尿片的小孩和卡通人物，與C朗作配對，另外亦有網民留言：「C朗在比賽中最大的貢獻就是拉高短褲。」、「C朗的短褲高過球迷對葡萄牙的期望。」最終C朗主射的那個罰球，卻以偏離目標收場。<br />\n<br />\n烏拉圭憑前鋒卡雲尼在上下半場各建一功，以2:1力克有比比頭槌建功的葡萄牙，躋身8強將硬撼法國。賽後，C朗拒絕談論自己的國際賽未來。"},{"pid":"75e291d39b84fb77f6bd657a91fb6cea0c2f8d03","tid":725333,"uid":19660,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T16:16:46.000Z","msg":"醜人多百怪"},{"pid":"b51d1a82f141a4e1a5f3881556bcb12eec06cc5f","tid":725333,"uid":35176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75e291d39b84fb77f6bd657a91fb6cea0c2f8d03","tid":725333,"uid":19660,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T16:16:46.000Z","msg":"醜人多百怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T16:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e1f7d37414876ae135f062f8920ccdbe0571ab","tid":725333,"uid":53731,"like":1,"d